"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-life-style-olympics-2024-alexis-ohanian-flavor-flav-rent-b2590003.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  'I will send payment TODAY so you do not have to worry bout,' Flavor Flav tells the track and field star  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Alexis OhanianandFlavor Flavhave revealed that they paid track and field Olympian Veronica Fraley's rent.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999547394519, \"rank\": 4.525800948156462e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Veronica_Lodge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6349868760316434e-14, \"text\": \"Veronica\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Veronica_Lodge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Veronica_Lodge\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Team USA startook to X,formerly known as Twitter, on August 1 to reveal that she did not have the funds at this time to pay her rent.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4057195778872996e-24, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also noted that the financial issue came as she's preparing to compete in this year's Olympics.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I compete in the Olympic Games TOMORROW and can not even pay my rent,\\\" the Vanderbilt University athlete tweeted.\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 874, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanderbilt_University\", \"score\": 0.9983181348827668, \"rank\": 0.0016792584653048724, \"text\": \"Vanderbilt University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanderbilt_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanderbilt_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My school only sent about 75 percent of my rent while they pay football players (who have not won anything) enough to buy new cars and houses.\\\"\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She later clarified her frustrations about not being able to afford her rent, adding: \\\"Thanks for the supporting messages but I want to clarify my irritation is not with the school itself, mainly the rules that bar me from making the amount I am WORTH as a collegiate athlete such as NIL which favors popularity over performance.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1343, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2487586048939108e-22, \"text\": \"NIL\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's all I am sayin.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wish me luck tm!\\\"\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After her tweet went viral, Ohanian did not hesitate to respond and offer to help out,writing: \\\"Got you!\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"DM me your $cashtag.\\\"\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He then tagged Flavor Flav -the sponsor for the US women's and men's water polo team-\\u00a0 and asked for his assistance, tweeting: \\\"C'mon now!\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9979370064138834, \"rank\": 0.0011648717667202097, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will split it with@flavorfav.\\\"\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the Reddit founder's post about Flavor Flav came after the singer made his own offer to help Fraley pay her rent.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reddit\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\"}, {\"begin\": 1773, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3086708562464574e-33, \"text\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I gotchu, DM me and I will send payment TODAY so you do not have to worry bout it TOMORROW, and imma be rooting for ya tomorrow LETZ GO!!!\\\"\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1867, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deutsche_Mark\", \"score\": 0.9996861576070449, \"rank\": 0.00031374513953201754, \"text\": \"DM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deutsche_Mark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deutsche_Mark\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ohanian then responded to his own tweet, where he discussed splitting the rent with Flavor Flav, and wrote: \\\"Update!\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2082, \"end\": 2093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3086708562464574e-33, \"text\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is done.\\\"\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He then showed a screenshot of the $7,760 payment he sent to the Olympian on Venmo, which included a note that read: \\\"'MURICA,\\\" along with the American flag and gold medal emojis.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2193, \"end\": 2201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999547394519, \"rank\": 4.525800948156462e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2205, \"end\": 2210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venmo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Venmo\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venmo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venmo\"}, {\"begin\": 2271, \"end\": 2284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999998831299, \"rank\": 1.0604899757915462e-10, \"text\": \"American flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flavor Flavthen re-sharedthe screenshot of Ohanian's Venmo payment and wrote: \\\"HERO, absolute hero!!!\\\"\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2362, \"end\": 2367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venmo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Venmo\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venmo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venmo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking toThe Daily Beast, a representative for the musician confirmed that the Olympian accepted his money and the two of them \\\"have been messaging.\\\"\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2494, \"end\": 2502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999547394519, \"rank\": 4.525800948156462e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The representative also clarified that Ohanian gave Fraley the money after Flavor Flav already paid her rent.\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2640, \"end\": 2651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3086708562464574e-33, \"text\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Flav paid her rent in full.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexis one upped him and sent her $7,760 - in honor of the name of his company,\\\" the representative said, referring to the name of Ohanian's technology company, Seven Seven Six.\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also issued a statement in an email to the publication about wanting to support major athletes.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just down to help those in need who are representing all of us.\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 3052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the type of awareness I have been trying to bring to these Olympians,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Independenthas contacted representatives for Flavor Flav and Ohanian for comment.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3191, \"end\": 3202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3086708562464574e-33, \"text\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flavor Flav has continued to be vocal about advocating for fellow Olympians.\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3305, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, two months before he officially announced his sponsorship with the US Water Polo teams, he'd already shared his plans to work with them on social media.\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3382, \"end\": 3384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9979370064138834, \"rank\": 0.0011648717667202097, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When team captain Maggie Steffens paid tribute to her teammates and expressed her love for her gruelingsport in a tribute on Instagramin May, she also highlighted the constant financial struggle for most Olympic athletes.\", \"from\": 3468, \"to\": 3689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3486, \"end\": 3501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maggie Steffens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flavor Flav then made his way to the comments of her post, where he first publicly shared that he wanted to sponsor thewomen's sportsteam.\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"AYYY YOOO, as a girl dad and supporter of all women's sports - imma personally sponsor you my girl, whatever you need.\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And imma sponsor the whole team,\\\" he wrote.\", \"from\": 3950, \"to\": 3993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My manager is in touch with your agent and imma use all my relationships and resources to help all you all even more.\", \"from\": 3994, \"to\": 4112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a FLAVOR FLAV promise.\\\"\", \"from\": 4113, \"to\": 4143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4145, \"to\": 4375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4196, \"end\": 4207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6301158733864853e-16, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"